# Silence direnv log output (export diff, status lines, etc.)
# The env var path has no "-" sentinel handling (unlike direnv.toml),
# so empty string is the correct value here. Note: direnv reads
# DIRENV_LOG_FORMAT before evaluating .envrc, so this only takes effect
# on subsequent loads. The authoritative setting is in
# ~/.config/direnv/direnv.toml.
export DIRENV_LOG_FORMAT=""

use flake
